dc_title_s: Leases & Contract Agreement Extents, The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission: Prince George's County, Maryland
dc_description_s: This dataset captures the spatial extents of the various leases and agreements entered into by M-NCPPC with various other public and private entities. All of these sites have had formal agreements signed by all parties, and in some cases the agreement has been recorded in land records. Most records in this feature class are sites where M-NCPPC has is the lesser and the transaction takes place on M-NCPPC property. The Prince George's County Planning Department does not have the authority to release this data. Please contact the authoritative source for more information and to acquire the data.
dc_creator_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission
